Package: customerRelationship
Title: Customer Relationship Timeline Processing
Version: 0.0.900
Authors@R: 
    person("Patrikios", "", email = "Patrikios@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Efficiently processes customer relationship data to identify and merge 
    consecutive periods with gaps using Rcpp for performance and data.table for 
    scalability. Calculates timeline relationships from raw transaction data.
